  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/smartphones/\" rel=\"tag\">智能手机</a></p><center><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/06/19/htc-butterfly-s-hands-on-tw/\"><img src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/06/htcbutterflysc1.jpg\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: solid; margin: 4px;\" /></a></center>\n<br />\n<br />\n今天我们看到 HTC <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/06/19/htc-butterfly-s-launch-tw/\">端出</a> 2013 年第二款旗舰手机 Butterfly s。从产品线来看，Butterfly 系列无疑和 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/HtcOne/\">One</a> 系列有着截然不同的美学观点。虽然在薄型化的风潮下，你总是可以从手机侧面找出一丝相似。不过从细部观察，Butterfly s 有着较多装饰线条，加上搭载了 BoomSound 前置双喇叭，成为上下对称的 ㄇ 字装饰，为正面带来更强的立体化视觉感受。由於 5 吋屏幕尺寸较大的缘故，让两边削薄的手感也更强烈。而拜窄边框设计之赐，Butterfly s 单手握持的操控性仍有不错的表现。就请跳转全文，来看更多动手玩细节。<br />\n<div class=\"postgallery\"><p><strong>Gallery: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/htc-butterfly-s-hands-on/\">HTC Butterfly s hands-on</a></strong></p><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/htc-butterfly-s-hands-on/5974304/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/06/htcbutterflysgallery1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/htc-butterfly-s-hands-on/5974305/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/06/htcbutterflysgallery2_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/htc-butterfly-s-hands-on/5974336/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/06/htcbutterflysgallery25_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/htc-butterfly-s-hands-on/5974312/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/06/htcbutterflysgallery6_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/htc-butterfly-s-hands-on/5974309/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/06/htcbutterflysgallery4_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a></div><p><br /><p class=\"continueReading\